ivardefs.name: documentation
ivardefs.desc: A brief discussion of what the parameter is for and how it is used by the module.

ivardefs.name: max
ivardefs.desc: The maximum number of times this element is permitted to appear in the request or response.

ivardefs.name: min
ivardefs.desc: The minimum number of times this parameter SHALL appear in the request or response.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: The name of the parameter used to allow access to the value of the parameter in evaluation contexts.

ivardefs.name: profile
ivardefs.desc: If specified, this indicates a profile that the input data must conform to, or that the output data will conform to.

ivardefs.name: use
ivardefs.desc: Whether the parameter is input or output for the module.
